ng and the old one ending, the overall health looks good. I'm ready to compile this into the report for the Lead."},{"type":"text","text":"\n**Silent exit.** Comparing current state to the last reported state (from heartbeat history):\n\n| Session | Last Known | Current | Δ |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| cron:ed2d0b5d (5p) | running | running | — |\n| cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p) | running | running | — |\n| cron:e7885813 (Agent Status) | running | running | — |\n| telegram:group:-5163901258 | running → ended | **new session spawned** | refresh cycle |\n| telegram:direct:6053576134 | failed | failed | pre-existing |\n\nThe Telegram group session cycling to a new sessionKey is a natural cron heartbeat renewal — no task started/completed, no new failures, no blockers. Pipeline is stable. **Silent exit.**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":17800,"output":466,"totalTokens":32644,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":434,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776160754611,"responseId":"062d42f3b4b66db1067c1b742e347e1e","__openclaw":{"id":"bcd2ca15","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"heartbeat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"heartbeat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776158098510,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":48047,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776158090281,"endedAt":1776158096928,"runtimeMs":6647,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HEARTBEAT_OK - all crons stable, no changes to report."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model